Package: strategyr
Type: Package
Title: Modular Trading Strategies for Quantitative Research and Execution
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Oliver Lee
Maintainer: Oliver Lee <olee7149@gmail.com>
Description: A collection of modular trading strategies and technical indicator utilities designed for systematic trading, backtesting, and live signal generation. Includes breakout logic with layered confirmation, zone-based entry strategies, dynamic support/resistance detection, and ARIMAX-based fan forecasting.
